‚úÖ 1. Architecture Summary
This dashboard follows Microsoft Fabric‚Äôs medallion architecture. 
Raw CSVs are ingested into the Bronze Lakehouse, cleaned in the Silver Warehouse, and curated in the Gold Warehouse with a Date table. 
The semantic model connects via DirectQuery for real-time insights.

‚úÖ 2. Pipeline Flow
A Fabric Data Pipeline automates ingestion, transformation, and semantic refresh across all layers. 
Each step is modular and monitored, ensuring reliable data delivery and KPI accuracy.

‚úÖ 3. Troubleshooting Wins
During development, I resolved schema mismatches between Dataflow Gen2 and Warehouse, 
rebuilt the Date table to support Month Sort and time intelligence, 
and optimized DirectQuery performance through semantic modeling best practices.

‚úÖ 4. KPI Logic Highlights
KPIs like YoY Growth, YoY %, and KPI vs Target are powered by custom DAX measures. 
These metrics enable executive storytelling and performance tracking across fiscal periods.

